unil De Silva, Christian Stoff, Erik Strong, Panpaka Supakalin, Hirohito Toda, Yuqing Xing, Xianbin Yao and Marin Yari. The team\u2019s appreciation goes to ILO, UNIFEM, UNESCO, UNICEF and WHO for their valuable and substantive inputs for the preparation of the report. The report was edited by Peter Stalker. It was designed by Marie Ange Holmgren-Sylvain. Wannaporn Sridama provided all administrative support.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "e46c6402-f0ec-4ab0-8056-ea152b46eb32": {"__data__": {"id_": "e46c6402-f0ec-4ab0-8056-ea152b46eb32", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-mdg-report-2009/2010", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Asia-Pacific MDG Report 2009/2010", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-mdg-report-2009/2010", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "2fe560be0edfa9c056162db9e649db4d4b8a8daa4a464638648aa48e36e8cdce"}, "2": {"node_id": "3aa6bd54-da97-4973-9563-edd22edcda3b", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-mdg-report-2009/2010", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "62a3a7bc8f87ce426c702b9f2f32db62236f041d9fc7e97ba9e1826a9bb3a0ac"}}, "hash": "d486009305ec270b4040293fa31b37a8ed6102fa67868a8ac238583e289b939d", "text": "Wannaporn Sridama provided all administrative support. vii ACHIEVING THE MILLENNIUM DEVELOPMENT GOALS IN AN ERA 